Class FileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.FileManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSVFileManager, InformationFileManager

    public abstract class FileManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class FileManager is the base class for all kinds of file manager needed. The specific subclasses of FileManager are built in function of the specific kind of file to manage.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alessandro Giovannacci
